{"code":0,"data":[{"cid":18271,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Alice","permissions":["report"],"pid":3134,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"冲塔？","timestamp":1592841242,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":18276,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Bob","permissions":["report"],"pid":3134,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"广义上来说教育就是洗脑的一种类型，不只是我们的教育，西方的教育也这样","timestamp":1592841265,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":18292,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Carol","permissions":["report"],"pid":3134,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"统治者的意志嘛。这个问题到现在一直都有，任何国家都有。感觉很难再去还原了。况且那些所谓的真实又何尝没有叙述者的个人意志在其中的呢","timestamp":1592841351,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":18297,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Dave","permissions":["report"],"pid":3134,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"无 可 奉 告","timestamp":1592841387,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":18325,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Eve","permissions":["report"],"pid":3134,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"一切道德是统治阶级的道德","timestamp":1592841489,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":18351,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Francis","permissions":["report"],"pid":3134,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"你听到的所有官方新闻都是或多或少有修饰的","timestamp":1592841576,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":18366,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Grace","permissions":["report"],"pid":3134,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"看到别的国家篡改历史的时候 不可避免的怀疑自身","timestamp":1592841613,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":18390,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":true,"name":"洞主","permissions":["report"],"pid":3134,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"所以咱们能举一些例子吗？比如说关于三年自然灾害有多少是真·灾害，有多少是人为造成的呢？","timestamp":1592841764,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":18424,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Hans","permissions":["report"],"pid":3134,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re 洞主:  这个话题不便于在中文互联网讨论，至少是不便于在墙内讨论。","timestamp":1592841933,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":18459,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Eve","permissions":["report"],"pid":3134,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re 洞主: 不走流程了，直接三七开","timestamp":1592842099,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":18555,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Isabella","permissions":["report"],"pid":3134,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"真相还重要吗，人一辈子几十年，蒙在鼓里过得舒舒服服，何必头破血流地去寻找真相呢。代价太大了，付不起。","timestamp":1592842523,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":18790,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Jason","permissions":["report"],"pid":3134,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"几乎所有社会都在做这件事，只不过具体内容各不相同。洗脑事很自然的操作，虽然未必是正当的。","timestamp":1592843619,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":19427,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Kate","permissions":["report"],"pid":3134,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"你如果不专门从事相关工作，又怎么能知道什么是真的什么是假的？你愿意相信，它就是真的。不愿意相信，它就是假的","timestamp":1592848341,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":19544,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Louis","permissions":["report"],"pid":3134,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re 洞主: 三年自然灾害的提法现在基本上不用了，现在都是说“三年困难时期”。这个说法改变，就是说人为失误为主，主要是“大跃进”和人民公社化运动的失误。单纯自然灾害是不会连续困难三年的。以及这三年之后接的是“调整，巩固，充实，提高”。","timestamp":1592852647,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":52802,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Margaret","permissions":["report"],"pid":3134,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re 洞主: 你可以去看看温铁军的十次危机，B站有视频","timestamp":1593249868,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":52811,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Margaret","permissions":["report"],"pid":3134,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re 洞主: 这里面和苏联脱钩和工业农业剪刀差有一定关系","timestamp":1593249902,"type":"text","url":""}],"post":{"attention":false,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"likenum":14,"permissions":["report","fold"],"pid":3134,"reply":16,"tag":"政治相关","text":"今天关于政治的话题比较多，我也来问一个吧。\n大家觉得从小到大，我们受到的教育有多少是属于洗脑的呢，我们有多少历史事件是被蒙在鼓里或者扭曲虚构了的呢？","timestamp":1592841203,"type":"text","updated_at":1618225410,"url":"","vote":{}}}